WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:center
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:00.650 --> 00:00:05.110
Lady Toki, we just received
news of Lord Oden's death...

3
00:00:05.110 --> 00:00:07.860
They say that he died a hero...

4
00:00:18.750 --> 00:00:20.380
"Toki...

5
00:00:20.380 --> 00:00:22.840
I feel my end approaching.

6
00:00:24.750 --> 00:00:26.920
If I fail to defeat him...

7
00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:31.010
one who can defeat Kaido
will not appear for some time.

8
00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:34.220
Twenty years from now,

9
00:00:34.810 --> 00:00:40.310
there will likely come a massive war,
terrible enough to split the seas themselves.

10
00:00:41.810 --> 00:00:44.690
That means, after twenty years,

11
00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:50.410
the primary figures of that massive war
will surge into the New World.

12
00:00:50.410 --> 00:00:54.120
They will be the ones to strike down Kaido!

13
00:00:54.530 --> 00:00:57.540
A long winter is coming to Wano.

14
00:00:58.830 --> 00:01:02.580
Toki, I want you to use your power...

15
00:01:02.580 --> 00:01:05.210
if I am to die."

16
00:01:14.760 --> 00:01:19.020
I entrust you with Enma and Ame no Habakiri.

17
00:01:19.020 --> 00:01:21.390
Give these swords to our children.

18
00:01:21.390 --> 00:01:25.440
I think they're still a little
too young to handle a sword...

19
00:01:26.730 --> 00:01:29.650
Are you not sad? I have been
sentenced to death!

20
00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:32.950
You are not going to die, are you?

21
00:01:35.780 --> 00:01:38.200
You are indeed my wife!

22
00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.630
My tears would only amuse you.

23
00:01:46.210 --> 00:01:49.800
We are not your weak spot.

24
00:01:50.210 --> 00:01:52.630
Keep watch, Oden.

25
00:01:53.430 --> 00:01:55.720
Look twenty years into the future.

26
00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:02.630
Open up the borderless map, then

27
00:02:02.630 --> 00:02:05.830
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

28
00:02:05.830 --> 00:02:10.220
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

29
00:02:10.220 --> 00:02:13.210
Riding on the wind

30
00:02:18.340 --> 00:02:22.550
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

31
00:02:22.740 --> 00:02:25.520
So don't you grow disheartened

32
00:02:25.830 --> 00:02:29.280
Laugh the tears away through the storm

33
00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:33.710
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

34
00:02:34.050 --> 00:02:36.310
That’s what your friends are there for

35
00:02:36.340 --> 00:02:38.470
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

36
00:02:38.470 --> 00:02:42.390
your crew will always have your back

37
00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:46.490
Even in the face of utter darkness

38
00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:49.480
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

39
00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:53.270
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

40
00:02:53.490 --> 00:02:56.260
Open up the borderless map, then

41
00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:59.120
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

42
00:02:59.420 --> 00:03:03.700
All great journeys starts with a single step

43
00:03:03.770 --> 00:03:04.710
DREAMIN’ ON

44
00:03:04.710 --> 00:03:07.490
Open up the borderless map, then

45
00:03:07.490 --> 00:03:10.230
Raise the flag we swore to defend

46
00:03:10.380 --> 00:03:13.120
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

47
00:03:13.190 --> 00:03:17.590
Just be true to yourself until the end

48
00:03:17.720 --> 00:03:22.430
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

49
00:03:32.230 --> 00:03:36.110
<b>The Kozuki Clan</b>

50
00:03:36.110 --> 00:03:38.240
Up you go!

51
00:03:39.450 --> 00:03:42.290
Stop! That's too high, Oden!

52
00:03:42.290 --> 00:03:45.960
Even from way up here in the sky,
you can't see everything.

53
00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:50.130
That is what the world is like,
Momonosuke and Hiyori.

54
00:03:50.790 --> 00:03:55.420
Feast your eyes! You will not find
sights like these in Wano.

55
00:03:58.430 --> 00:04:01.600
It shines just like treasure!

56
00:04:01.600 --> 00:04:03.390
Treasure, huh?

57
00:04:03.390 --> 00:04:05.390
Funny you would mention that.

58
00:04:05.390 --> 00:04:07.730
You are indeed my son.

59
00:04:07.730 --> 00:04:10.610
Broaden your knowledge, Momonosuke.

60
00:04:10.610 --> 00:04:15.110
I shall teach you everything I know.

61
00:04:16.570 --> 00:04:19.700
What type of girls do you like?

62
00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:21.160
He's too young for that!

63
00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:25.910
Just think of people as fish cakes
and slice them up, Momonosuke!

64
00:04:25.910 --> 00:04:27.250
What are you teaching him?!

65
00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:38.670
You have improved, Hiyori.

66
00:04:38.670 --> 00:04:40.890
I like that song!

67
00:04:40.890 --> 00:04:42.010
Really?!

68
00:04:42.010 --> 00:04:44.310
It's called Moon Princess!

69
00:04:48.100 --> 00:04:50.270
I'll try to get even better!

70
00:04:50.770 --> 00:04:52.610
What a beautiful song.

71
00:04:52.610 --> 00:04:55.150
Please play it at my funeral.

72
00:05:01.410 --> 00:05:02.950
Hey, Momo!

73
00:05:02.950 --> 00:05:04.700
Do not make your sister cry!

74
00:05:04.700 --> 00:05:06.700
You made her cry!

75
00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.710
From what I said earlier?

76
00:05:09.710 --> 00:05:12.170
Sorry, I was just kidding!

77
00:05:13.580 --> 00:05:14.540
You were?!

78
00:05:16.670 --> 00:05:18.880
I will not die!

79
00:05:19.880 --> 00:05:22.590
How was the outside world?

80
00:05:23.890 --> 00:05:26.810
Well, long story short...

81
00:05:28.390 --> 00:05:31.100
it was the best adventure ever!

82
00:05:31.100 --> 00:05:32.980
Did you stop by Zou?

83
00:05:32.980 --> 00:05:35.400
Yes! I did indeed!

84
00:05:36.110 --> 00:05:41.280
Zou and the Kozuki Clan historically
have a strong bond with each other.

85
00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:43.990
The minks are tough warriors.

86
00:05:43.990 --> 00:05:45.990
Keep that in mind, guys.

87
00:05:45.990 --> 00:05:49.160
When in a pinch, head for Zou!

88
00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:52.080
I am certain they will be of tremendous help.

89
00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:54.710
Lord Oden, what do you mean by "in a pinch"?

90
00:05:54.710 --> 00:05:57.960
What do I mean? A pinch is a pinch.

91
00:05:57.960 --> 00:06:00.340
I am counting on you two as well.

92
00:06:00.340 --> 00:06:02.630
Meow I'm embarrassed.

93
00:06:02.630 --> 00:06:05.850
Let's work even harder, Cat.

94
00:06:08.220 --> 00:06:09.930
Everyone!

95
00:06:09.930 --> 00:06:11.390
Do not fret!

96
00:06:11.810 --> 00:06:14.440
I collected all of these for you.

97
00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:15.560
Well, now!

98
00:06:15.900 --> 00:06:20.110
For the future of this country,
you all must survive!

99
00:06:20.650 --> 00:06:22.610
We are in your debt, Shinobu.

100
00:06:23.530 --> 00:06:24.910
What a boon.

101
00:06:24.910 --> 00:06:27.330
Please, do not mention it...

102
00:06:27.330 --> 00:06:29.790
We are heading to Oden Castle in Kuri!

103
00:06:30.410 --> 00:06:31.410
Follow me!

104
00:06:31.410 --> 00:06:33.040
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

105
00:06:43.050 --> 00:06:44.800
Say, Sir Kin...

106
00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:48.430
Do you think I can be
a retainer for the Kozuki Clan?

107
00:06:48.430 --> 00:06:51.850
We are all self-proclaimed retainers.

108
00:06:51.850 --> 00:06:53.560
The choice is yours!

109
00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:55.560
Thank you!

110
00:07:00.860 --> 00:07:03.150
I found them! Here they are!

111
00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:07.070
Wipe out the Kozuki bloodline!

112
00:07:08.620 --> 00:07:09.450
Kiku!

113
00:07:09.450 --> 00:07:10.200
Right!

114
00:07:22.250 --> 00:07:23.760
Shut up!

115
00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:25.470
What?!

116
00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:29.390
You traitorous bastard,
sympathizing with enemies!

117
00:07:29.390 --> 00:07:33.680
Are you-gara the spy that Kaido
was talking about, Dog?!

118
00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:35.310
Screw you!

119
00:07:35.310 --> 00:07:38.560
This all happened because
you provoked Kaido and Orochi!

120
00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:42.070
You-gara might as well have killed Lord Oden!

121
00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:43.150
What?!

122
00:07:46.990 --> 00:07:49.280
I will take everyone to Zou!

123
00:07:49.280 --> 00:07:52.990
If I let you, we'd all be dead
before we got there!

124
00:07:58.750 --> 00:08:00.920
Inuarashi! Nekomamushi!

125
00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:02.550
That's enough!

126
00:08:04.590 --> 00:08:06.170
Doggy! Kitty!

127
00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:07.840
Those idiots!

128
00:08:08.340 --> 00:08:09.510
Let go of me!

129
00:08:11.970 --> 00:08:13.390
What is that?!

130
00:08:13.390 --> 00:08:16.100
Leave them to their fate!
Time is of the essence!

131
00:08:16.100 --> 00:08:18.140
Too many enemies...

132
00:08:18.140 --> 00:08:20.350
Give me a hand, Ashura!

133
00:08:20.350 --> 00:08:21.190
Okay!

134
00:08:26.690 --> 00:08:29.160
Denjiro! Ashura!

135
00:08:33.450 --> 00:08:34.950
I can go to their aid!

136
00:08:35.370 --> 00:08:36.540
Run!

137
00:08:37.870 --> 00:08:40.670
To Oden Castle!

138
00:08:47.590 --> 00:08:48.880
Use fire arrows!

139
00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:52.010
Mother...!

140
00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:55.100
It will be all right!

141
00:08:55.100 --> 00:08:57.730
I must see to it that you both escape!

142
00:08:58.310 --> 00:08:59.730
There is a way out of this!

143
00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.450
Mother!

144
00:09:18.660 --> 00:09:20.830
Mother!

145
00:09:30.380 --> 00:09:33.510
Mother! Mother!

146
00:09:38.020 --> 00:09:39.180
What is your name?

147
00:09:45.110 --> 00:09:47.110
I'll fall!

148
00:09:47.110 --> 00:09:49.740
It's too high! I'm scared...

149
00:09:49.740 --> 00:09:51.860
I'll die!

150
00:09:53.990 --> 00:09:57.200
Your father was a fool of a lord.

151
00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:02.080
The Kozuki Clan will end with your death...

152
00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:03.790
No, it won't!

153
00:10:05.540 --> 00:10:09.760
Your father is a great man, and you will...

154
00:10:10.630 --> 00:10:14.510
My father was a great samurai...

155
00:10:15.140 --> 00:10:16.800
and the one you are holding...

156
00:10:18.180 --> 00:10:26.060
is the man who will one day lead this country!

157
00:10:34.570 --> 00:10:39.160
Hollow words and a dream
someone put in your mouth...

158
00:10:39.700 --> 00:10:42.080
I didn't know you were so young...

159
00:10:44.170 --> 00:10:45.670
Father!

160
00:10:46.330 --> 00:10:48.750
Somebody, help me!

161
00:10:56.340 --> 00:10:58.390
I've lost interest...

162
00:11:08.900 --> 00:11:12.190
I can't believe that's Oden's son!

163
00:11:12.190 --> 00:11:14.990
Join the ashes of this burning castle!

164
00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.210
Please forgive me!

165
00:11:27.210 --> 00:11:29.460
Even though we were with him...

166
00:11:29.460 --> 00:11:31.170
we could do nothing as Lord Oden–

167
00:11:31.170 --> 00:11:33.050
Raise your heads.

168
00:11:33.050 --> 00:11:36.260
Lady Toki, this place
is dangerous! We must leave!

169
00:11:37.590 --> 00:11:39.600
I am staying.

170
00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.010
You cannot!

171
00:11:42.010 --> 00:11:44.350
Let us leave the castle together!

172
00:11:44.350 --> 00:11:45.560
Lady Toki!

173
00:11:45.560 --> 00:11:48.810
We will protect you for as long as we breathe!

174
00:11:48.810 --> 00:11:50.190
Lady Toki!

175
00:11:50.730 --> 00:11:53.780
You must escape... to the future.

176
00:11:54.610 --> 00:11:55.740
The future?

177
00:12:09.500 --> 00:12:10.790
Don't let her get away!

178
00:12:10.790 --> 00:12:12.090
Kill her!

179
00:12:19.260 --> 00:12:20.390
Damn!

180
00:12:25.020 --> 00:12:29.350
Toki, you are seeking after it too, are you not?

181
00:12:29.350 --> 00:12:33.820
From 800 years ago, seeking the day
when the world turns upside down...

182
00:12:35.530 --> 00:12:38.570
Just jump twenty years into the future!

183
00:12:38.570 --> 00:12:39.530
What you seek is–

184
00:12:41.030 --> 00:12:44.160
No dinner for you today, Oden.

185
00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:45.290
What?!

186
00:12:45.290 --> 00:12:49.790
Well, I earn no money,
so it stands to reason...

187
00:12:49.790 --> 00:12:50.790
That is not why!

188
00:12:52.330 --> 00:12:54.630
What?! Then I do not understand...

189
00:12:54.630 --> 00:12:56.800
What you said to me was truly awful!

190
00:12:56.800 --> 00:13:00.760
<b>Bakura Town


Kuri</b>

191
00:13:02.760 --> 00:13:06.100
I'm scared, Grandma.

192
00:13:06.100 --> 00:13:08.100
Something feels different tonight...

193
00:13:08.100 --> 00:13:09.690
It's over...

194
00:13:09.690 --> 00:13:12.600
We'll receive divine punishment...

195
00:13:13.060 --> 00:13:17.900
because we didn't put our faith in
the Kozuki Clan and Lord Oden.

196
00:13:20.530 --> 00:13:25.700
The endless night begins...

197
00:13:30.500 --> 00:13:32.330
Oden...

198
00:13:32.330 --> 00:13:34.840
I came fleeing from the past.

199
00:13:35.500 --> 00:13:40.670
I always thought if I jumped
to the future, someone would...

200
00:13:41.430 --> 00:13:42.930
would do it...

201
00:13:50.350 --> 00:13:51.310
Lady Toki.

202
00:13:55.150 --> 00:13:58.320
You are the moon, unaware
of the approach of daybreak.

203
00:13:58.690 --> 00:14:00.820
May your purpose be fulfilled...

204
00:14:09.660 --> 00:14:15.920
and cast nine shadows on
the night woven of twenty years.

205
00:14:15.920 --> 00:14:22.220
Then you shall know the brilliance of dawn!

206
00:14:42.150 --> 00:14:43.610
Oden...

207
00:14:51.910 --> 00:14:54.790
I told you to boil the water!

208
00:14:55.330 --> 00:14:57.210
It's already boiling, Lord Orochi!

209
00:14:58.630 --> 00:15:00.750
No, it isn't!

210
00:15:00.750 --> 00:15:02.760
It's cold!

211
00:15:02.760 --> 00:15:04.090
It's cold, it's cold...

212
00:15:05.470 --> 00:15:06.550
It's hot!

213
00:15:08.180 --> 00:15:10.680
Lord Orochi, it's already scalding hot!

214
00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:12.890
You'll get burned!

215
00:15:13.770 --> 00:15:15.310
Shut up!

216
00:15:15.310 --> 00:15:17.100
I'm so cold!

217
00:15:17.100 --> 00:15:19.940
I can't stop shaking!

218
00:15:19.940 --> 00:15:23.320
Bring me the bones of the Kozuki samurai!

219
00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:25.360
Why can't you find them?!

220
00:15:25.360 --> 00:15:28.740
Show me proof of their deaths!

221
00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:35.080
"Twenty years"?

222
00:15:35.790 --> 00:15:37.370
Lady Toki...

223
00:15:38.790 --> 00:15:41.130
Are they alive?

224
00:15:45.380 --> 00:15:48.430
Princess! This is the Kappa Dance!

225
00:16:39.350 --> 00:16:41.440
Hey, you!

226
00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:44.520
Look at what the cat dragged in!

227
00:16:44.520 --> 00:16:47.780
Do you really live here in the capital?

228
00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:02.040
Hey, please wait!

229
00:17:02.040 --> 00:17:03.710
You're quite strong!

230
00:17:03.710 --> 00:17:05.210
Where are you from?

231
00:17:05.210 --> 00:17:07.090
Let us be your followers!

232
00:17:07.090 --> 00:17:08.420
What's your name?

233
00:17:16.270 --> 00:17:17.680
My name?

234
00:17:18.930 --> 00:17:20.560
Let's see...

235
00:17:22.310 --> 00:17:23.810
Kyoshiro!

236
00:17:23.860 --> 00:17:23.940
<b>yoshiro Kyoshiro</b>

237
00:17:23.940 --> 00:17:27.110
<b>Kyoshiro</b>

238
00:17:39.710 --> 00:17:41.790
So you guys are the Kyoshiro Family...

239
00:17:41.790 --> 00:17:42.710
Yes, lord!

240
00:17:43.750 --> 00:17:45.590
Lift up your head!

241
00:17:49.170 --> 00:17:51.680
I've heard good things about you.

242
00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:54.550
How would you like to serve as my guard?

243
00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:58.060
It would be an honor, Lord Orochi!

244
00:17:59.180 --> 00:18:01.600
Good, good! That's great!

245
00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:05.610
In that case, money, women, soldiers...

246
00:18:05.610 --> 00:18:08.940
I can provide everything you need!

247
00:18:09.360 --> 00:18:12.150
Very nice! Very nice!

248
00:18:15.530 --> 00:18:18.830
Too good to be true! Who is he?!

249
00:18:18.830 --> 00:18:21.330
He's well connected and knows how to fight!

250
00:18:21.330 --> 00:18:25.380
A man of chivalry has stepped up
to fill Boss Hyogoro's shoes!

251
00:18:26.460 --> 00:18:29.090
The Kyoshiro Family
dominates the Flower Capital!

252
00:18:29.090 --> 00:18:31.090
He has a weakness, too!

253
00:18:31.090 --> 00:18:33.340
Yeah, he always looks sleepy...

254
00:18:33.340 --> 00:18:36.090
So people call him Napping Kyoshiro!

255
00:18:36.090 --> 00:18:37.680
Probably too much nightlife!

256
00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:50.230
It's the Witching Hour Boy!

257
00:18:50.570 --> 00:18:53.570
He stole money from the storehouse!

258
00:18:56.110 --> 00:18:59.160
<b>The Witching Hour Boy</b>

259
00:19:02.660 --> 00:19:04.830
Lady Hiyori!

260
00:19:04.830 --> 00:19:06.670
Your Highness!

261
00:19:06.670 --> 00:19:09.130
Where did you go?!

262
00:19:13.920 --> 00:19:14.970
Boss!

263
00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:21.470
A cute girl has been
hanging around out front...

264
00:19:21.470 --> 00:19:24.100
She must be an orphan who
slipped into the capital...

265
00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:27.150
The poor thing is starving...

266
00:19:29.650 --> 00:19:31.940
This must be hard to understand...

267
00:19:31.940 --> 00:19:34.150
What?! Denjiro?!

268
00:19:34.150 --> 00:19:35.150
It's really you?!

269
00:19:35.150 --> 00:19:36.660
Yes, it is true.

270
00:19:37.280 --> 00:19:38.530
Lady Hiyori.

271
00:19:40.660 --> 00:19:42.580
Denjiro...

272
00:19:43.290 --> 00:19:46.330
I see... So Kawamatsu took care of you.

273
00:19:46.960 --> 00:19:50.710
My face is possessed by
the phantom of wrath...

274
00:19:50.710 --> 00:19:54.460
to the point that even Kin'emon
and the others wouldn't recognize me.

275
00:19:54.460 --> 00:19:56.380
But that suits my purposes!

276
00:19:57.300 --> 00:20:00.850
Until the day of the decisive battle...

277
00:20:02.220 --> 00:20:05.480
do not tell anyone about me, even our allies.

278
00:20:05.980 --> 00:20:10.020
In place of Kawamatsu,
I will protect you from now on!

279
00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:15.030
You must now call yourself Komurasaki!

280
00:20:18.070 --> 00:20:20.200
Take this, Sir Witching Hour.

281
00:20:21.320 --> 00:20:23.030
I came into some more money.

282
00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:27.080
Do not be reckless...

283
00:20:27.710 --> 00:20:31.420
I will make sure to distribute it in Ebisu Town.

284
00:20:32.630 --> 00:20:34.050
Listen.

285
00:20:34.050 --> 00:20:39.470
As I have said many times, you must carry
fake blood under your kimono at all times.

286
00:20:40.220 --> 00:20:43.470
Orochi is obsessed with you...

287
00:20:43.470 --> 00:20:46.180
but unaware that you are
Lord Oden's daughter...

288
00:20:46.600 --> 00:20:48.020
That must be tough for you.

289
00:20:48.030 --> 00:20:53.060
In case of an emergency, I will tear
Komurasaki away from Orochi with death.

290
00:20:53.690 --> 00:20:58.820
And convince the people of
the Flower Capital that Komurasaki is dead.

291
00:21:00.530 --> 00:21:02.490
I will be fine. We are so close...

292
00:21:03.990 --> 00:21:05.290
It has almost been...

293
00:21:05.910 --> 00:21:07.160
twenty years!

294
00:21:07.950 --> 00:21:12.080
And now it's almost the present day...

295
00:21:12.750 --> 00:21:20.090
A few months before Luffy's raid
on the night of the Fire Festival...

296
00:21:15.210 --> 00:21:20.090
<b>A Few
Months
Before
the Fire
Festival</b>

297
00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:23.510
They're here!

298
00:21:23.850 --> 00:21:26.930
The ghosts are really here!

299
00:21:29.020 --> 00:21:32.810
So Toki's power was real!

300
00:21:32.810 --> 00:21:39.740
Kin'emon, Kanjuro, Raizo,
Kikunojo, and Momonosuke...

301
00:21:39.740 --> 00:21:40.990
Five of them!

302
00:21:41.400 --> 00:21:44.830
They jumped from that day
twenty years ago!

303
00:21:45.530 --> 00:21:48.870
Is there really a power like that?

304
00:21:48.870 --> 00:21:50.580
From that burning castle?

305
00:21:51.290 --> 00:21:54.380
It's not just someone's idea
of a joke to freak you out?

306
00:21:54.380 --> 00:21:55.420
Look!

307
00:21:55.420 --> 00:21:57.340
Look at this letter!

308
00:21:57.340 --> 00:21:58.670
Look, look...

309
00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:11.690
Go monitor the sea coast!

310
00:22:11.690 --> 00:22:13.810
Someone will try to leave the country!

311
00:22:13.810 --> 00:22:14.480
– My lord!
– My lord!

312
00:22:14.480 --> 00:22:19.030
If they're alive, don't finish them off.

313
00:22:19.030 --> 00:22:24.910
After twenty years, there's something
I wanna ask the remnants of the Kozuki...

314
00:22:27.330 --> 00:22:32.290
At any rate, your spy is quite competent.

315
00:22:32.290 --> 00:22:37.000
Listen, he's a trustworthy man...

316
00:22:42.220 --> 00:22:46.600
He was born and raised in a theater troupe.

317
00:22:46.600 --> 00:22:48.050
But one day,

318
00:22:48.510 --> 00:22:50.680
as a result of persecution in Wano,

319
00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:54.270
he lost his parents while they were on stage.

320
00:22:54.690 --> 00:22:57.900
They're kin of the daimyo killer!

321
00:22:57.900 --> 00:22:59.520
Serves them right!

322
00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:01.360
Yeah! Yeah!

323
00:22:59.980 --> 00:23:01.360
They had it coming!

324
00:23:04.320 --> 00:23:08.830
He survived by constantly changing masks.

325
00:23:08.820 --> 00:23:11.950
<b>You're a descendant of the Kurozumi Clan's main family?!</b>

326
00:23:11.950 --> 00:23:13.120
That's right.

327
00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:16.960
I erased your parents'
murderers from existence.

328
00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:21.840
But the curtains have only
just risen on our tale of revenge!

329
00:23:21.840 --> 00:23:24.720
Live your life as a true Kozuki retainer,

330
00:23:25.090 --> 00:23:30.350
and die as a Kozuki retainer
without a single soul noticing!

331
00:23:32.770 --> 00:23:37.900
That's the important role you've
been given on this grand stage!

332
00:23:37.900 --> 00:23:39.770
Can you play the part?

333
00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:45.650
<b>I've been looking for a place to die...</b>

334
00:23:47.030 --> 00:23:49.490
<b>It would be an honor.</b>

335
00:23:51.490 --> 00:23:55.500
His only pleasure is to play someone else.

336
00:23:56.040 --> 00:23:59.130
Every time I went to Oden Castle
to borrow money,

337
00:23:59.130 --> 00:24:04.300
he brought out twice
the amount that I asked for.

338
00:24:04.300 --> 00:24:08.220
I could ally with you only
because I had that money...

339
00:24:08.220 --> 00:24:12.600
I'm sure the information about that fool
Oden's raid was helpful for you, too.

340
00:24:13.600 --> 00:24:15.640
He was such a fanatic...

341
00:24:15.640 --> 00:24:18.650
that he was truly ready to die...

342
00:24:19.560 --> 00:24:22.610
with Oden and the others in the execution.

343
00:24:22.980 --> 00:24:25.490
He has no will of his own.

344
00:24:25.490 --> 00:24:30.030
Until I stop him, he'll live
as a true Kozuki retainer,

345
00:24:30.030 --> 00:24:33.370
discreetly sending information all the while.

346
00:24:34.040 --> 00:24:36.960
He's so faithful, it's almost eerie.

347
00:24:40.830 --> 00:24:43.210
<b>Flower

Capital



Present

Day</b>

348
00:24:50.010 --> 00:24:54.310
And now, the legend of the samurai
has passed down to posterity.

349
00:24:58.100 --> 00:25:01.770
It's been twenty years since
Kozuki Oden's tragic death.

350
00:25:02.190 --> 00:25:05.980
This is the tale of two fated rivals,
the Kozuki and the Kurozumi,

351
00:25:05.980 --> 00:25:08.950
and the pirate Kaido!

352
00:25:09.820 --> 00:25:14.490
To fulfill Kozuki Oden's dream of
opening up the borders...

353
00:25:19.580 --> 00:25:23.000
the samurai retainers leaped
twenty years into the future.

354
00:25:32.720 --> 00:25:37.350
For months, they risked their lives
to recruit allies who would fight with them.

355
00:25:41.140 --> 00:25:47.690
Their persistence was rewarded
because 4,200 people stood up to fight!

356
00:25:48.320 --> 00:25:50.240
With weapons and ships!

357
00:25:50.240 --> 00:25:52.910
Troops now gather at Tokage Port,

358
00:25:52.910 --> 00:25:56.740
ready for the raid at twilight,
the night of the Fire Festival.

359
00:25:57.160 --> 00:25:59.870
Head for Onigashima!

360
00:25:59.870 --> 00:26:01.080
Kaido...

361
00:26:04.330 --> 00:26:06.670
We're gonna kick your ass!

362
00:26:06.670 --> 00:26:08.170
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

363
00:26:12.130 --> 00:26:14.140
That's how it was supposed to be...

364
00:26:14.140 --> 00:26:16.140
Stop, all of you!

365
00:26:16.140 --> 00:26:19.430
Taking that small boat is suicide!

366
00:26:20.850 --> 00:26:23.690
If we miss this opportunity...

367
00:26:24.020 --> 00:26:26.770
we will have to wait another year.

368
00:26:27.440 --> 00:26:32.200
Kaido's entire army will hunt down the rebels.

369
00:26:35.530 --> 00:26:36.780
Do not go!

370
00:26:37.620 --> 00:26:40.160
I forbid you to go!

371
00:26:41.190 --> 00:26:42.540
Kin'emon!

372
00:26:42.540 --> 00:26:50.300
Ashura! Kanjuro! Raizo!
Kiku! Kawamatsu! Inuarashi!

373
00:26:51.420 --> 00:26:56.590
None of the expected 4,200 troops arrived,

374
00:26:56.590 --> 00:26:59.760
and there were signs
of destruction at the port...

375
00:27:00.470 --> 00:27:02.100
The weather is raging!

376
00:27:02.560 --> 00:27:04.440
There is no way out!

377
00:27:06.310 --> 00:27:09.820
Wait! Are you all just giving up?!

378
00:27:09.820 --> 00:27:10.820
Everyone!

379
00:27:12.030 --> 00:27:15.910
We are not giving up, Lord Momonosuke!

380
00:27:17.910 --> 00:27:21.040
Our low numbers will allow us to sneak in,

381
00:27:21.040 --> 00:27:25.250
and point a sword at Kaido's neck
before anyone realizes!

382
00:27:28.040 --> 00:27:31.670
As long as we live, we will not give up!

383
00:27:37.510 --> 00:27:39.390
Something is not right!

384
00:27:40.600 --> 00:27:44.730
This means our plan has been leaked... again!

385
00:27:44.730 --> 00:27:49.980
I was thinking... No, I am sure
everyone was thinking the same!

386
00:27:50.980 --> 00:27:53.530
I did not want to consider it...

387
00:27:55.320 --> 00:27:59.160
but one of us is probably a spy!

388
00:28:01.830 --> 00:28:04.700
At this point, I do not even want to know!

389
00:28:05.540 --> 00:28:08.750
Sir Kin! This is unlike you!

390
00:28:08.750 --> 00:28:12.750
You find the spy,
cut them down, and move on!

391
00:28:12.750 --> 00:28:15.420
Otherwise, we cannot move forward!

392
00:28:16.130 --> 00:28:18.930
There is no way they will confess!

393
00:28:20.300 --> 00:28:23.060
Kiku is correct, Kin!

394
00:28:23.060 --> 00:28:24.720
Let us clear it all up!

395
00:28:32.610 --> 00:28:34.690
By acknowledging that it was me!

396
00:28:36.950 --> 00:28:38.780
Kanjuro?!

397
00:28:41.070 --> 00:28:42.950
That's not funny...

398
00:28:42.950 --> 00:28:46.660
We were almost boiled to death together!

399
00:28:47.370 --> 00:28:48.790
That we were.

400
00:28:48.790 --> 00:28:52.840
And I could have fulfilled the role
of a lifetime if we had all died!

401
00:28:53.670 --> 00:28:56.170
One of the Nine Red Scabbards...

402
00:28:56.170 --> 00:29:00.090
Kanjuro of the Evening Shower
who pledged his loyalty to Oden...

403
00:29:00.090 --> 00:29:03.350
That man was nothing but a facade!

404
00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:22.450
I shared joys and sorrows with all of you
every day and earned your complete trust...

405
00:29:22.450 --> 00:29:26.160
I never hated any of you
and meant you no harm.

406
00:29:26.580 --> 00:29:32.130
I just kept sending
information to Lord Orochi...

407
00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:36.670
So you would claim it has all been
a lie from the very beginning?

408
00:29:36.670 --> 00:29:38.260
Why would you do that?!

409
00:29:39.380 --> 00:29:42.090
My real name is...

410
00:29:43.340 --> 00:29:45.470
Kurozumi Kanjuro!

411
00:29:47.220 --> 00:29:49.560
Need I say more?

412
00:29:51.190 --> 00:29:53.980
The first plan was leaked...

413
00:29:53.980 --> 00:29:57.900
not because Law's men let it slip...

414
00:29:58.610 --> 00:30:01.150
Yasuie covered it up beautifully...

415
00:30:01.150 --> 00:30:05.200
and changed the rendezvous point
in exchange for his life.

416
00:30:05.200 --> 00:30:07.330
That was impressive...

417
00:30:07.330 --> 00:30:13.170
But once I got the message,
his death became meaningless.

418
00:30:18.380 --> 00:30:23.890
When Jack showed up at
the elusive Zou without a vivre card,

419
00:30:23.890 --> 00:30:27.180
you wondered why, didn't you, Inuarashi?

420
00:30:35.100 --> 00:30:38.070
Why did you not suspect any of us?!

421
00:30:42.820 --> 00:30:46.780
How could you not realize
it was one of your own?!

422
00:30:47.120 --> 00:30:49.160
You knew something was off!

423
00:30:49.160 --> 00:30:52.250
All this time! About everything!

424
00:31:10.850 --> 00:31:12.890
Hey, it was true!

425
00:31:12.890 --> 00:31:17.520
Lord Orochi said there'd be a group of
enemies heading to Onigashima in a boat!

426
00:31:18.650 --> 00:31:20.570
That's too hilarious!

427
00:31:20.570 --> 00:31:24.280
No way! They really are
the Red Scabbards from way back!

428
00:31:24.280 --> 00:31:27.030
And one of them is our spy!

429
00:31:28.700 --> 00:31:30.370
Would that be you?!

430
00:31:30.370 --> 00:31:31.450
Yes, indeed.

431
00:31:32.120 --> 00:31:34.000
Kanjuro!

432
00:31:47.340 --> 00:31:54.640
Taking my secret to our watery grave
would have been my dream performance,

433
00:31:54.980 --> 00:31:58.020
but then Lord Orochi stopped me.

434
00:31:58.020 --> 00:32:01.820
He said, "Good job. The play is over.

435
00:32:01.820 --> 00:32:05.320
Bring Momonosuke to Onigashima!"

436
00:32:06.400 --> 00:32:09.280
Kin'emon!

437
00:32:09.280 --> 00:32:11.160
Lord Momonosuke!

438
00:32:11.490 --> 00:32:13.910
How did Kanjuro get back to the port?!

439
00:32:15.660 --> 00:32:17.170
Then this is...

440
00:32:20.960 --> 00:32:22.340
A drawing?!

441
00:32:25.210 --> 00:32:28.470
The Kanjuro that we know
can't draw like this...

442
00:32:41.230 --> 00:32:43.610
Wow, you guys.

443
00:32:43.610 --> 00:32:46.150
How can you sleep through all of this?!

444
00:32:46.150 --> 00:32:47.280
Honestly!

445
00:32:48.570 --> 00:32:50.490
Is the ship repaired?

446
00:32:55.080 --> 00:32:59.330
I'm always strongest
right after I eat and take a nap!

447
00:33:00.540 --> 00:33:01.540
What?!

448
00:33:01.540 --> 00:33:03.090
Fire!

449
00:33:06.630 --> 00:33:07.760
Don't tell me...!

450
00:33:07.760 --> 00:33:10.380
Sorry for being a little late!

451
00:33:10.800 --> 00:33:12.180
Who is that?!

452
00:33:12.180 --> 00:33:15.510
I thought we sank all the enemy ships!

453
00:33:18.270 --> 00:33:20.060
There's something in the water!

454
00:33:25.480 --> 00:33:29.950
What kind of idiots take a rowboat
out to sea in the middle of a storm?!

455
00:33:29.950 --> 00:33:32.030
What?! He is...!

456
00:33:32.030 --> 00:33:34.620
Respect the sea, you samurai dumbasses!

457
00:33:34.620 --> 00:33:35.370
Hey!

458
00:33:38.910 --> 00:33:40.870
This time from the other side!

459
00:33:41.210 --> 00:33:45.550
I saw a ridiculous number of ships and samurai
gathering at the other port.

460
00:33:45.550 --> 00:33:46.880
Who are they?!

461
00:33:46.880 --> 00:33:48.880
A-And he is...!

462
00:33:51.800 --> 00:33:55.260
I was about to sink them
to get them out of my way!

463
00:33:59.810 --> 00:34:01.480
Sir Luffy!

464
00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:03.060
You are all okay?!

465
00:34:04.610 --> 00:34:06.940
So you came after all, Jaggy!

466
00:34:08.400 --> 00:34:12.240
Straw Hat! Kaido's head is mine!

467
00:34:18.540 --> 00:34:21.500
What in the world is going on?

468
00:34:31.380 --> 00:34:33.630
Why did I not hear about any of this?!

469
00:34:34.050 --> 00:34:36.300
Luffy!

470
00:34:36.300 --> 00:34:38.220
This isn't what we were told!

471
00:34:39.890 --> 00:34:43.520
Our only order was to sink
a boat with a few samurai!

472
00:34:44.940 --> 00:34:47.190
Aren't these guys pirates?!

473
00:34:48.940 --> 00:34:52.110
Those Worst Generation guys
are supposed to be in jail!

474
00:34:52.570 --> 00:34:54.160
You guys!

475
00:34:54.160 --> 00:34:56.950
Why are you picking on
some samurai in a rowboat?!

476
00:35:06.290 --> 00:35:09.000
The sea is where pirates fight!
